/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_0.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|my father,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I offer it to you.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1000.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And say, have they not risen?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1002.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as vultures gather round a dying ox?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1005.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|they will come true,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1006.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and mine is the song of a people that is doomed.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1008.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But of these other words I will speak in their place.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1011.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I went to my mother.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1013.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Presently she raised herself from the ground and sat up with her hands over her face.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1017.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The blood from the wound the stick had made ran down her face on to her breast,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_102.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|There he was thrown in with men who,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1021.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|She sat for a long while thus,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1023.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|while the child cried,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1025.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the cow lowed to be milked,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1026.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I wiped up the blood with the grass.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1029.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|At last she took her hands away and spoke to me.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1031.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she said,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1032.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I have dreamed a dream.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1033.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he was grown like a giant.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1035.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|his eyes blazed like the lightning,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1037.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He caught up people after people in his hands and tore them,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_104.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for thirty or forty years,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1041.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Before him was the green of summer,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1043.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I saw our people, Mopo;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1045.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|they were many and fat,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1046.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|their hearts laughed,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1048.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the men were brave,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1049.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the girls were fair;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1050.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I counted their children by the hundreds.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1052.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I saw them again, Mopo.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1054.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|thousands of bones tumbled together in a rocky place,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1058.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1059.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|stood over the bones and laughed till the earth shook.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_106.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|had been intimately acquainted with the Zulu people,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1062.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|You alone were left of our people.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1064.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and with you came others,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1065.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|You stabbed him with a little spear,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1067.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he fell down and grew small again;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1070.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he fell down and cursed you.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1072.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|your sister-and he died.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1074.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So we rose and went home.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1076.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But I held my peace, for I was afraid, very much afraid.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1081.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and died quickly.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1083.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then my mother fell down and died,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1085.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I cried very much,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1087.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for I loved her,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1088.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and it was dreadful to see her cold and stiff,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_109.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|with their history,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1091.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|with not a word to say however loudly I called to her.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1095.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Well, they buried my mother, and she was soon forgotten.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1099.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I only remembered her,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_11.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|a song has been sung in my ears of how first you mastered this people of the Zulu.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_110.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and their customs.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1100.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|nobody else did-not even Baleka,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1104.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for she was too little-and as for my father he took another young wife and was content.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_111.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|From these he heard many tales and traditions,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1110.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|After that I was unhappy,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1112.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for my brothers did not love me,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1113.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|because I was much cleverer than they,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1115.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and was swifter in running;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1117.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|so they poisoned the mind of my father against me and he treated me badly.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1123.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for we were both lonely,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1124.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and she clung to me like a creeper to the only tree in a plain,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1128.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and though I was young,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1129.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|that to be wise is to be strong,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1132.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|yet he whose mind directs the battle is greater than he who kills.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1137.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now I saw that the witch-finders and the medicine-men were feared in the land,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_114.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|are rarely told nowadays,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1141.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and that everybody looked up to them,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1143.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|even when they had only a stick in their hands,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1146.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|ten men armed with spears would fly before them.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1149.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So I learned the arts of the medicine-men.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1152.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I made sacrifices,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1154.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I did all those things of which you have heard,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1156.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I learned much;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1158.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for there is wisdom in our magic as well as lies-and you know it,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_116.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and in time to come may cease to be told altogether.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1162.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|my father,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1163.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|else you had not come here to ask me about your lost oxen.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1167.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So things went on till I was twenty years of age-a man full grown.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1172.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|By now I had mastered all I could learn by myself,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1175.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|so I joined myself on to the chief medicine-man of our tribe,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1179.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|who was named Noma.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1180.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He was old, had one eye only, and was very clever.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1184.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Of him I learned some tricks and more wisdom,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1188.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but at last he grew jealous of me and set a trap to catch me.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_119.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|now that nation has been destroyed,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1192.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|a rich man of a neighbouring tribe had lost some cattle,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1196.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and came with gifts to Noma praying him to smell them out.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1199.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then the headman grew angry and demanded back his gifts;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1203.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and hot words passed.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1204.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I said, for I feared that blood would be shed.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1208.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"You are nothing but a boy,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1209.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|answered the headman.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_121.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and the chief aim of its white rulers is to root out the warlike spirit for which it was remarkable,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1211.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Can a boy have wisdom?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1212.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"That shall soon be known,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1214.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I said, taking the bones in my hand.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1217.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|throwing them something as we throw dice.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1219.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Leave the bones alone!"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1221.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|We will ask nothing more of our snakes for the good of this son of a dog.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1224.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"He shall throw the bones,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1226.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|answered the headman.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1227.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And he lifted his spear.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1229.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then I made haste to begin; I threw the bones.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1233.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The headman sat on the ground before me and answered my questions.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1236.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|my father-how sometimes the witch-doctor has knowledge of where the lost things are,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1241.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for our ears are long,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1243.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as but the other day it told me of your oxen.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1246.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Well, in this case, my snake stood up.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1249.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I knew nothing of the man's cattle,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1251.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and told them to him one by one,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1253.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and how one of them had fallen into a stream and lay there on its back drowned,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1257.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the man was pleased,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1258.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and said that if my sight was good,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1261.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he found the cattle,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1262.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the gifts should be taken from Noma and given to me;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1265.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he asked the people who were sitting round,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1268.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and there were many,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1269.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|if this was not just.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_127.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and to replace it by a spirit of peaceful progress.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1270.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Yes, yes,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1271.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|they said, it was just, and they would see that it was done.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1275.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He knew that I had made a true divination, and he was very angry.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1280.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It was a big matter:
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1282.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the herd of cattle were many,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1283.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|then all men would think me the greater wizard.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1286.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now it was late,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1287.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and the moon had not yet risen,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1290.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|After that he went away.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1291.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I too went into my hut and lay down to sleep.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1295.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Suddenly I awoke, feeling a weight upon my breast.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1298.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I fell back again and looked.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_130.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|perhaps the most wonderful that the world has seen,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1300.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the moon lay low on the sky like a ball of fire far away.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1304.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He was seated across me,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1306.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and in his hand was a knife.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1308.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he hissed into my ear,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1310.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Very well, now I will show you how I serve such puppies.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1313.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|so that you cannot squeal,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1315.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|then I will cut you to pieces slowly,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1318.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and in the morning I will tell the people that the spirits did it because you lied.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1323.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Next, I will take off your arms and legs.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1325.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Yes, yes, I will make you like a stick!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1328.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then I will
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1329.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he began driving in the knife under my chin.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_133.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|is already a thing of the past;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1332.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Mercy, my uncle,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1334.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Will you do this?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1335.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he asked, still pricking me with the knife.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1337.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Will you get up,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1338.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and hide them there?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_134.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|building it up from the smallest beginnings.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1340.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And he named a secret valley that was known to very few.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1343.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|If you do that, I will spare you and give you three of the cows.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1348.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|by my father's spirit,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1350.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I will find a way to kill you!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1352.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Certainly I will do it, my uncle,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1353.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I answered.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1354.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Why did you not trust me before?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1356.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Had I known that you wanted to keep the cattle,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1359.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I would never have smelt them out.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1361.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"You are not so wicked as I thought,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1363.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Get up, then, and do my bidding.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1365.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|You can be back here two hours after dawn.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1368.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So I got up,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1369.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|thinking all the while whether I should try to spring on him.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_137.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|When he appeared at the commencement of this century,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1373.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But I was without arms, and he had the knife;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1376.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|also if,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1377.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I prevailed and killed him,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1378.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So I made another plan.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1380.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I would go and find the cattle in the valley where I had smelt them out,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1384.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but I would not bring them to the secret hiding-place.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1387.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|my father,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1388.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and all the people.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1389.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He had not been a witch-doctor till he grew old for nothing.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1393.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He had planted me by him like a tree,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1396.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but he meant to keep me clipped like a bush.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1399.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now I had grown tall and overshadowed him;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_140.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|it was as the ruler of a single small tribe;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1402.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I went to the corner of my hut,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1404.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Noma watching me all the while,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1406.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then I started through the moonlight.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1408.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I began to run,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1410.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|singing to myself as I went,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1411.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|to frighten away the ghosts,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1413.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|For an hour I travelled swiftly over the plain,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1416.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|till I came to the hillside where the bush began.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1419.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Here it was very dark under the shade of the trees,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_142.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|when he fell,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1422.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I sang louder than ever.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1424.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|At last I found the little buffalo path I sought, and turned along it.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1429.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Presently I came to an open place,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_143.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|in the year eighteen twenty eight,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1431.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|where the moonlight crept in between the trees.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1434.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I knelt down and looked.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1436.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|sometimes whispering and sometimes talking out loud.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1440.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Here the trail of the cattle was broad:
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1442.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|they had broken down the ferns with their feet and trampled the grass.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1446.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Presently I came to a pool.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1448.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And there at the edge of the pool floated the drowned ox,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_145.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as he is called also,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1453.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I stepped forward and looked round.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1455.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|My eye caught something;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1456.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|As I looked, one of them snorted, rose and shook the dew from his hide.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_146.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and in his march to power he had slaughtered more than a million human beings.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1461.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He seemed big as an elephant in the mist and twilight.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1464.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as Noma had bid me.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1466.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But I would not do this.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1468.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and tell all men that Noma was a thief.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1470.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|As I sat, I heard a noise, and looked up.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1473.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|came a crowd of men,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1475.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and leading them was Noma,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1477.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and by his side the headman who owned the cattle.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1480.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I rose and stood still, wondering;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1482.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but as I stood,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1483.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|they ran towards me shouting and waving sticks and spears.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1487.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|screamed Noma.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1488.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|There he is!-the clever boy whom I have brought up to bring shame on me.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1493.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|What did I tell you?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1494.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Did I not tell you that he was a thief?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1496.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Yes-yes!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1497.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he is stealing the cattle!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1499.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He knew where they were all the time,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1501.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and now he is taking them away to hide them.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1504.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They would be useful to buy a wife with,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1506.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|my clever boy?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1507.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I understood now, my father.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_151.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|so no more need be said of them here.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1510.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|My heart went mad in me,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1511.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|everything began to swim round,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1513.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|a red cloth seemed to lift itself up and down before my eyes.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1518.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I have always seen it thus when I was forced to fight.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1521.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I screamed out one word only,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1524.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I yelled again, and rushed on at the headman.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1526.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He got up his shield,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1528.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but I knocked it down upon his head,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_153.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|has been to convey,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1530.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and over he rolled senseless.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1532.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Whether he lived or died I do not know, my father;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1535.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but his head being of the thickest, I think it likely that he lived.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_154.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|in a narrative form,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1540.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|while the people stood astonished,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1542.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I turned and fled like the wind.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1544.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|throwing spears at me and trying to cut me off.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1547.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I went like the wind;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1549.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and presently the sound of their chase grew fainter and fainter,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_155.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and to make accessible,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1553.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|till at last I was out of sight and alone.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1556.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|then I went and hid in a patch of reeds down by a swamp.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1560.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|All day long I lay there thinking.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1562.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|What was I to do?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1564.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now I was a jackal without a hole.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1566.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|If I went back to my people,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1568.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|certainly they would kill me,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_157.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|in a popular shape,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1570.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|whom they thought a thief.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1571.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and that I did not wish,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1573.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|though my heart was sad.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1575.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the boy to whom I had given the cup of water long ago.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1578.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I had heard of him: his name was known in the land;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_158.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|incidents of history which are now,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1582.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|already the air was big with it;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1584.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the very trees and grass spoke it.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1586.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The words he had said and the vision that my mother had seen were beginning to come true.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1592.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|so that nobody could find them any more.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1594.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I thought to myself that I would arise and go to him.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1598.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Perhaps he would kill me; well, what did it matter?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_16.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And when they grew weary,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_160.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|only to be found in a few scarce works of reference,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1602.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Certainly I should be killed if I stayed here.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1604.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Yes, I would go.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1605.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But now my heart pulled another way.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1608.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|There was but one whom I loved in the world-it was my sister Baleka.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1613.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|My father had betrothed her to the chief of a neighbouring tribe,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1617.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but I knew that this marriage was against her wish.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1620.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Perhaps my sister would run away with me if I could get near her to tell her that I was going.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1624.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I would try-yes, I would try.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1627.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I waited till the darkness came down,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1630.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for I was very hungry,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1631.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Some of my people were seated outside of a hut,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1634.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|talking together over a fire.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1636.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I crept near, silently as a snake, and hid behind a little bush.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_164.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|rarely consulted,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1641.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I knew that they could not see me outside the ring of the firelight,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1645.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I wanted to hear what they said.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1647.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|As I guessed, they were talking of me and called me many names.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_165.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It will be obvious that such a task has presented difficulties,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1652.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Just then a dog that was lying by the fire got up and began to sniff the air.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1656.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I could not see what dog it was-indeed,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1659.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|that is what comes of want of experience, my father.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1663.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The dog sniffed and sniffed,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1665.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|then he began to growl,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1666.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|looking always my way,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1668.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I grew afraid.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1669.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"What is the dog growling at?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1671.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|said one man to another.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1673.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But the other man was taking snuff and did not like to move.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1676.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Let the dog go and see for himself,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1679.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he answered, sneezing,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_168.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and think with the mind and speak with the voice of a Zulu of the old regime.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1680.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"what is the good of keeping a dog if you have to catch the thief?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1683.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|said the first man to the dog.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1685.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And he ran forward, barking.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1687.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as I lay not knowing what to do,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1690.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|stopped barking,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1691.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I whispered to him.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1692.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And he lay down by my side.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1694.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Where has that dog gone now?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1696.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|said the first man.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1698.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|that he stops barking suddenly and does not come back?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_17.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|did you not stand and say,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1700.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"We will see,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1701.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|said the other, rising, a spear in his hand.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1705.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now once more I was terribly afraid,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1708.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|or I must run for my life again.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1710.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But as I sprang up to run,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1712.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|a big black snake glided between the men and went off towards the huts.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1717.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They jumped aside in a great fright,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1719.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|then all of them turned to follow the snake,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1722.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|saying that this was what the dog was barking at.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1725.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|my father,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1726.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|which without any doubt took the shape of a snake to save my life.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_173.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|their details have, therefore, been suppressed.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1731.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|At first I thought that I would kill him, lest he should betray me;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1735.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he sat down upon the ground wagging his tail,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1738.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So I thought that I would take my chance, and we went on together.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1742.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|This was my purpose:
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1744.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|would be empty,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1745.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I came to the reed fence that surrounded the huts.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1748.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Nobody was to be seen at the gate,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_175.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Still much remains,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1750.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|which was not shut with thorns as usual.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1753.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It was my duty to close it, and I had not been there to do so.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1757.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|bidding the dog lie down outside,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1759.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I stepped through boldly,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1761.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|reached the door of my hut,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1763.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and listened.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1764.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It was empty; there was not even a breath to be heard.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1767.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|which was so nicely carved that I did not like to leave it.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_177.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|may be invited to leave this book unread.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1771.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Soon I found them.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_1773.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then I felt about for my skin rug,
