/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_227.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Also the writer's thanks are due to his friends,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_229.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|late Zulu border agent,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_231.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for much information given to him in bygone years by word of mouth,
