/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_242.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|is an historical weapon,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_243.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He was an arbitrary person, for
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_246.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|no matter what was discussed in our village,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_248.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he would bring it to a conclusion with a stick.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_250.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But he made a good end;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_252.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for when the Zulu soldiers attacked him,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_254.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he killed no less than twenty of them with the Watcher,
