/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_281.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|just before the Zulu war,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_283.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|revealing something or other which had a great effect throughout the land,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/30min/6097_286.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I know that the Zulus were quite impressed that some calamity was about to befall them.
